data.description: Welcome Home!! This beautiful ranch has so much potential to offer! The home has 4 oversized bedrooms,2 Full baths, 2 half baths, and has over +3000 sq.ft of living space to spread out. This home features a custom Better Homes and Garden floor plan w/ ample storage and large closets(master has large walk-in), LG bathroom w/soaking tub, and enormous living room w/ wood burning fp, first floor laundry, a huge walk-out basement w/ wood burning stove, a custom kitchen w/ a double oven, w/ many updates.The home sits on almost 2 acres w/ a peaceful stream that runs on the backside of the property.Enjoy the comfort of rural living while having all of your amenities close by.Septic pump, and clean 2022' aerator 21', water softener 23' LVT,Come turn this home into what your dreaming of!
